txt.en: '[placeholder], after claiming this tower, I expected all of the Rangers to check in, but I have not seen or heard from several of them. They could be in danger! Please, search for them. They must still be in the Circle of Madness.'
Some of the Rangers are missing, and Rhadrog would like help searching for them.
Ambushed Rangers can be found in the Circle of Madness.\n\nYou should rescue ambushed Rangers.
'The missing Rangers are all accounted for, thanks to you! I think they learned their lesson around the merrevail: always keep an eye on the skies!'
Rhadrog is stationed inside Barad Elenath, the Star-gazers' Spire.\n\nYou should talk to Rhadrog.
